Organics/ Megatron Revived:
 
Organics giggled again, and awaited the word to come inside.
 
Megatron looked out over the horizon.  He scanned the area, his sensors as strong as any ship's.  He was wary of the Predacon signatures, and the ever looming threat of Unicron.  He narrowed his optics, looking where Unicron hid behind Earth's blue sky.
"Can we go in now?  Is Rodimus even in there?" he asked impatiently.
